j359AHSLFXN7QXJI2w7Rm0BHy8esGSoxfiLTmsz_R2QTPLJgdJOu2fGvNouLmehpYGjhvex00eW3Q0aXjVSlpMktTF_UmPkWORcQU&amp;__tn__=EEHH-R</a><br />\n【男拔小學家長確診武肺 中小學明起停課】<br />\n<br />\n本台收到消息，拔萃男書院校方將向學生發通告，因附屬小學小三學生家長確診武肺，小學部及中學部明起開始停課，直至另行通知，明日起將重新採用視像教學。<br />\n<br />\n本港爆發第三波武漢肺炎疫情，單在今日就出現14宗確診個案，連同拔萃附小在內，現時至少有7間學校，有學生或家長確診或成密切接觸者因而宣佈要即時停課。香港演藝學院亦出現確診個案，今日亦一同緊急停課。另外，沙田區今日亦出現至少3宗確診個案，不排除有社區爆發風險。<br />\n<br />\n隨著武肺第三波疫情疑似爆發，不少議員已經要求教育局宣布提早放暑假，以減低進一步爆發的風險。<br />\n<br />\n文/J<br />\n<br />\n#DBC #加山傳播 #DBChannel #武漢肺炎 #停課了 #放暑假了"},{"pid":"5d66443f6eeb115f857de6f20ce0833568e30b70","tid":2098600,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:03:03.000Z","msg":"又係雙非<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c288d0c8aaf20be06f6b1c705959a036762fcbfb","tid":2098600,"uid":140538,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"67c31fcf34b5f76159ed753587ba77ab957b980c","tid":2098600,"uid":47614,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:01:17.000Z","msg":"一手？你就係個小學雞？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:06:14.000Z","msg":"係咪唔識咩叫一手料<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7c7775d5c69edb6bfe999ff418284c8613915a","tid":2098600,"uid":277502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T15:06:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/494910/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%8B%94%E8%90%83%E7%94%B7%E6%9B%B8%E9%99%A2%E9%99%84%E5%B1%AC%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E9%80%A3%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%AD%E5%AD%B8%E9%83%A8%E6%98%8E%E8%B5%B7%E5%81%9C%E8%AA%B2?utm_source=01appshare&amp;utm_medium=referral\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F494910%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%258B%2594%25E8%2590%2583%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%2599%25A2%25E9%2599%2584%25E5